# Navigation search registry

When you add, rename, or remove a **sidemeny link** in `*_index.html` (system, sikkerhet, brukere, cmdb, virksomhet, rapport), update the matching entry in [`systemoversikt/search_nav_pages.py`](systemoversikt/search_nav_pages.py):

- `label` – link text shown in the sidemeny
- `url_name` – Django URL name (must `reverse()` successfully)
- `keywords` – extra search terms (avoid bare generic words like `systemer` alone)
- `permissions` – match the target view's access requirements; use `[]` when the page has no permission check
- `url_for_user` – when the URL needs the current user's virksomhet or similar

Run `pytest systemoversikt/tests/test_search_nav_pages.py` after changes.
